{"tid":1619724,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"關於今晚開花，我有的好重要既事提醒大家。","createTime":"2019-10-04T08:29:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T08:40:11.000Z","uid":62011,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"120f45246bbbba4e12052b0f9ea9bfb5996533eb","tid":1619724,"uid":62011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T08:29:21.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">1. 無須事前公佈集合地點、時間。係時候考驗大家默契。<br />\n2. 各有各做，(注意陣地戰唔席關係我地強項)。<br />\n3. 清楚目標係，唔好為留而留，諗清楚做咩。達成目的走人，絕對唔可以被人拉。<br />\n4. 人多!!!!!<br />\n5. 保護好自己。<br />\n6. 必須有哨兵。<br />\n</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"1cee8f3894b418c7a2aca20c8578084be2f75407","tid":1619724,"uid":62011,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T08:31:25.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">目標對象係咩???<br />\n例如有份推動緊急法既民建聯、新民黨。及其他。</span></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"db08f44f896124bf0f534427f213214b6eaac7ea","tid":1619724,"uid":293667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T08:31:47.000Z","msg":"今晚出去前 先睇一睇<br />\n<br />\n［花10秒睇保護自已］千祈唔好以為啲狗好蠢 其實佢哋不斷做緊嘢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1617712\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1617712</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"86a067689d83ce2dcab3830a5a0d77a5d2cdac43","tid":1619724,"uid":35125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T08:31:50.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"083c346443eeac6a9fa386d95dca07b317ff4961","tid":1619724,"uid":70859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T08:35:30.000Z","msg":"唔好意思借個位<br />\n18區開花，唔好去政總<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1619215\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1619215</a><br />\n<br />\n行政署向政府總部的員工發電郵，指政總員工可以在今日下午3時半後下班。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">有政總員工表示，多名警察在午飯時間手持槍枝進入政總戒備。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1484230-20191004.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1484230-20191004.htm&d=pX%2F9NM0RDLHEoMpKo%2B7ToVQYB6qXEwX4CB7r1YlVkGU%3D&h=d003e769\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1484230-20191004.htm&h=9b6f7ca8\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1484230-20191004.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n金鐘佢地已經打到熟晒<br />\n知道晒我地有咩不足、點樣可以捉到最多人<br />\n而家已經有晒部署駐晒兵<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">我地唔好再打冇把握嘅仗，去返自己地頭，遍地開花！</span></strong>"},{"pid":"78f94b4d74e08fa0bd1b414ff37a5801e20885fc","tid":1619724,"uid":117225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1cee8f3894b418c7a2aca20c8578084be2f75407","tid":1619724,"uid":62011,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T08:31:25.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">目標對象係咩???<br />\n例如有份推動緊急法既民建聯、新民黨。及其他。</span></span></span></strong>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T08:40:11.000Z","msg":"最重要<br />\n無底線<br />\n反抗極權<br />\n要保命<br />\n但唔好怕 團結就係力量<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}